LastFuckingM - LastFM API 2.0

  my $xml = LastFuckingM::req("artist.getSimilar", artist => "Robbie Basho");

  $LastFuckingM::json = 1;
  my $data = LastFuckingM::req(...);

* Will do authorisation when required, see below
* Knows how to POST methods when necessary (eg track.scrobble)
* Returns XML or a data structure from JSON (

Gives a link to the user to authorise its own session and saves it for the future.
This could be done differently by altering various subroutines in a subclass or whatever.
